ports/doom — licensing and provenance
=====================================

This directory is a hand-translation of id Software's DOOM into the `bet`
language. It is a derivative work of id's released DOOM source and is
distributed under the GNU General Public License, version 2. The full license
text is in the file COPYING next to this notice.

    DOOM
    Copyright (C) 1993-1996 id Software, Inc.
